high_descs: Turn left, walk straight and then go to the coffee table to your left.
Pick up the cloth on the coffee table.
Turn around, walk straight past the microwave, hang a left and go to the sink to your right.
Put the cloth in the sink, rinse it off, and pick it back up.
Get out of the kitchen, turn right, walk straight and go to the shelf to your right.
Put the cloth in the shelf below the one with the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean cloth on the shelf.
